| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-3771 — Recovery Inhibition (darkrace)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: fd07df33-90e4-53ac-87c9-6d8bb9fb9be2"
